drm/exynos: atomic phase 3: use atomic .set_config helper

Now that phase 1 and 2 are complete switch .set_config helper to
use the atomic one.

v2: also remove .prepare() callback

v3: remove .mode_set() and .mode_set_base() and encoder's
.prepare() callbacks

